Download and extract
 https://github.com/rweigel/expandtemplate/archive/master.zip

Browser interface (no server required)
 Open index.htm with web browser.

Command-line (requires node.js)
 npm install
 node app.js tests.txt [check] [debug]

Server (requires node.js)
 npm install
 node app.js 8001; curl http://localhost:8001/app?template=&start=&stop=&type=&check=
 
Browser interface 
 http://localhost:8001/
 